1.title: Introduction
1.plot: In this course I will teach you how to initiate an out of body experience. This means that your consciousness will be able to move outside of your physical body and travel through the "Astral Plane". You will be able to go and visit any place you heart desires- including different cities all across the globe, secret installations, remote underground facilities, far away planets and much more.
